- cs.SI (Speech Processing) is also a likely category as the paper deals with the analysis of snore sounds, which can be considered as a type of speech signal.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a novel data augmentation approach based on semi-supervised conditional GANs, which is a type of machine learning technique.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with the development of automatic snore sound classification systems.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the classification of snore sounds, which can be considered as a type of language signal.
